<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>The title bar displays the <strong>user ID</strong> and <strong>user name</strong> as well as the <strong>date</strong> and <strong>time</strong> when changes were last made to the user account.<br>
The user ID is a distinct identification number for the user. It is assigned by the system and cannot be changed.</p>
