<p>Select the user class for the user. You can choose from the following classes: <strong>Admin</strong>, <strong>Variable</strong>, <strong>Call centre</strong>, <strong>API</strong>, <strong>Logistics</strong>, <strong>Blog</strong> and <strong>Newsletter2Go</strong>.</p>
</div></div></td>
