</div>
</div>
<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="47">2.3.5. Deleting a mailbox</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as described below to delete a mailbox. You need admin rights to delete mailboxes/aliases. After deleting a mailbox/alias, you need to wait 48 hours before you can create a new mailbox/alias with the email address that you just deleted.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock warning">
